OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome late
OL,6,Fsunny spells, then clear spells
OL,7,Fovernight, with showers, these
OL,8,Fbecoming fewer and lighter as the
OL,9,Fnight goes on. Touch of frost possible
OL,10,Fin sheltered spots.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FA few morning showers with
OL,13,Fsunny spells, but the afternoon looks
OL,14,Fdry with some longer spells of
OL,15,Fsunshine. Still rather cold with
OL,16,Fnorthwesterly winds remaining
OL,17,Foccasionally strong in coastal parts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
